      <title>Hexo+butterfly搭建个人博客</title>
      <link href="/Hexo-butterfly%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
      <url>/Hexo-butterfly%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="hexo常用指令"><a href="#hexo常用指令" class="headerlink" title="hexo常用指令"></a>hexo常用指令</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean        #清除缓存文件 (db.json) 和已生成的静态文件 (public)</span><br><span class="line">hexo g            #生成静态文件</span><br><span class="line">hexo d            #部署到网站   简化为 hexo g -d</span><br><span class="line">hexo s            #启动本地服务器</span><br><span class="line">hexo n &quot;title&quot;    #新建一篇文章,标题为title</span><br><span class="line">hexo version      #显示 Hexo 版本</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="准备工作"><a href="#准备工作" class="headerlink" title="准备工作"></a>准备工作</h2><p>​完成Hexo环境搭建，参考<a href="https://dora-cmon.github.io/posts/b8f4bd70/">Hexo博客搭建</a></p><p>​<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/21cfbf15/">官方文档</a></p><h2 id="安装Butterfly主题"><a href="#安装Butterfly主题" class="headerlink" title="安装Butterfly主题"></a>安装Butterfly主题</h2><p>​参考<a href="https://dora-cmon.github.io/posts/fad26ff2/">Hexo 配置butterfly主题</a></p><p>​<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/ncphoton/p/16950595.html">Hexo-Butterfly主题配置</a></p><h2 id="美化"><a href="#美化" class="headerlink" title="美化"></a>美化</h2><p>​参考<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/MoYu-zc/p/14395965.html">Butterfly美化</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
